android.permission.READ_SYNC_STATS.full_description: Allows an app to read the sync stats for an account, including the history of sync events and how much data is synced.

android.permission.INTERNET.full_description:
Allows the app to create
     network sockets and use custom network protocols. The browser and other
     applications provide means to send data to the internet, so this
     permission is not required to send data to the internet.

android.permission.BIND_VPN_SERVICE.full_description:
Allows the holder to bind to the top-level
        interface of a Vpn service. Should never be needed for normal apps.

android.permission.UPDATE_LOCK.full_description: Allows the holder to offer information to the system about when would be a good time for a noninteractive reboot to upgrade the device.

android.permission.BIND_INPUT_METHOD.full_description:
Allows the holder to bind to the top-level
        interface of an input method. Should never be needed for normal apps.

android.permission.ACCESS_CACHE_FILESYST.full_description: Allows the app to read and write the cache filesystem.

android.permission.INJECT_EVENTS.full_description:
Allows the app to deliver
        its own input events (key presses, etc.) to other apps. Malicious
        apps may use this to take over the phone.

android.permission.BIND_DEVICE_ADMIN.full_description:
Allows the holder to send intents to
        a device administrator. Should never be needed for normal apps.

android.permission.MODIFY_PHONE_STATE.full_description:
Allows the app to control the
        phone features of the device. An app with this permission can switch
        networks, turn the phone radio on and off and the like without ever notifying
        you.

android.permission.SET_PREFERRED_APPLICA.full_description:
Allows the app to
        modify your preferred apps. Malicious apps may
        silently change the apps that are run, spoofing your
        existing apps to collect private data from you.

android.permission.WRITE_PROFILE.full_description:
Allows the app to
      change or add to personal profile information stored on your device, such
      as your name and contact information.  This means the app can identify you
      and may send your profile information to others.

android.permission.SET_WALLPAPER_HINTS.full_description: Allows the app to set the system wallpaper size hints.

android.permission.REBOOT.full_description: Allows the app to force the phone to reboot.

android.permission.BROADCAST_PACKAGE_REM.full_description:
Allows the app to
        broadcast a notification that an app package has been removed.
        Malicious apps may use this to kill any other running
        app.

android.permission.ASEC_CREATE.full_description: Allows the app to create internal storage.

android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS.full_description:
Allows the app to modify the
        system's settings data. Malicious apps may corrupt your system's
        configuration.

android.permission.MANAGE_APP_TOKENS.full_description:
Allows the app to
        create and manage their own tokens, bypassing their normal
        Z-ordering. Should never be needed for normal apps.

android.permission.PACKAGE_VERIFICATION_.full_description:
Allows the app to verify a package is
        installable.

android.permission.CONFIRM_FULL_BACKUP.short_description: confirm a full backup or restore operation
android.permission.CONFIRM_FULL_BACKUP.full_description: Allows the app to launch the full backup confirmation UI.  Not to be used by any app.

android.permission.ASEC_ACCESS.full_description: Allows the app to get information on internal storage.

android.permission.USE_SIP.full_description: Allows the app to use the SIP service to make/receive Internet calls.

android.permission.READ_CALL_LOG.full_description:
Allows the app to read
      your phone's call log, including data about incoming and outgoing calls.
      This permission allows apps to save your call log data, and malicious apps
      may share call log data without your knowledge.

android.permission.CHANGE_NETWORK_STATE.full_description: Allows the app to change the state of network connectivity.

android.permission.SEND_SMS.full_description:
Allows the app to send SMS messages.
     This may result in unexpected charges. Malicious apps may cost you money by
     sending messages without your confirmation.

android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS.full_description: Allows the app to request authentication tokens.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.full_description:
Allows the app to
        have itself started as soon as the system has finished booting.
        This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the
        app to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.FLASHLIGHT.full_description: Allows the app to control the flashlight.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.full_description:
Allows the app to access the phone
      features of the device.  This permission allows the app to determine the
      phone number and device IDs, whether a call is active, and the remote number
      connected by a call.

android.permission.RECEIVE_MMS.full_description:
Allows the app to receive and process MMS
      messages. This means the app could monitor or delete messages sent to your
      device without showing them to you.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.full_description: Allows the app to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.STATUS_BAR_SERVICE.full_description: Allows the app to be the status bar.

android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS.full_description:
Allows the app to get
      the list of accounts known by the phone.  This may include any accounts
      created by applications you have installed.

android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD.full_description:
Allows the app to disable the
      keylock and any associated password security.  For example, the phone
      disables the keylock when receiving an incoming phone call, then
      re-enables the keylock when the call is finished.

android.permission.WRITE_MEDIA_STORAGE.full_description: Allows the app to modify the contents of the internal media storage.

com.android.voicemail.permission.ADD_VOI.full_description:
Allows the app to add messages
      to your voicemail inbox.

android.permission.BLUETOOTH_ADMIN.full_description:
Allows the app to configure
      the local Bluetooth phone, and to discover and pair with remote devices.

android.permission.RECEIVE_WAP_PUSH.full_description:
Allows the app to receive and process
     WAP messages.  This permission includes the ability to monitor or delete
     messages sent to you without showing them to you.

android.permission.SET_WALLPAPER.full_description: Allows the app to set the system wallpaper.

android.permission.GET_PACKAGE_SIZE.full_description: Allows the app to retrieve its code, data, and cache sizes

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.full_description: Allows the app to test a permission for the SD card that will be available on future devices.

android.permission.PERSISTENT_ACTIVITY.full_description: Allows the app to make parts of itself persistent in memory.  This can limit memory available to other apps slowing down the phone.

android.permission.VIBRATE.full_description: Allows the app to control the vibrator.

android.permission.PACKAGE_USAGE_STATS.full_description: Allows the app to modify collected component usage statistics. Not for use by normal apps.

android.permission.BIND_ACCESSIBILITY_SE.full_description:
Allows the holder to bind to the top-level
        interface of an accessibility service. Should never be needed for normal apps.

android.permission.MOUNT_UNMOUNT_FILESYS.full_description:
Allows the app to mount and
        unmount filesystems for removable storage.

android.permission.WRITE_CALL_LOG.full_description:
Allows the app to modify your phone's call log, including data about incoming and outgoing calls.
        Malicious apps may use this to erase or modify your call log.

android.permission.FACTORY_TEST.full_description:
Run as a low-level manufacturer test,
        allowing complete access to the phone hardware. Only available
        when a phone is running in manufacturer test mode.

android.permission.SET_TIME_ZONE.full_description: Allows the app to change the phone's time zone.

android.permission.SET_ORIENTATION.full_description:
Allows the app to change
        the rotation of the screen at any time. Should never be needed for
        normal apps.

android.permission.BROADCAST_STICKY.full_description:
Allows the app to
    send sticky broadcasts, which remain after the broadcast ends. Excessive
    use may make the phone slow or unstable by causing it to use too
    much memory.

android.permission.FORCE_STOP_PACKAGES.full_description: Allows the app to forcibly stop other apps.

android.permission.UPDATE_DEVICE_STATS.full_description:
Allows the app to modify
        collected battery statistics. Not for use by normal apps.

android.permission.BRICK.full_description:
Allows the app to
        disable the entire phone permanently. This is very dangerous.

android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE.full_description:
Allows the app to connect to and
      disconnect from Wi-Fi access points and to make changes to device
      configuration for Wi-Fi networks.

android.permission.RECEIVE_SMS.full_description:
Allows the app to receive and process SMS
      messages. This means the app could monitor or delete messages sent to your
      device without showing them to you.

android.permission.BIND_PACKAGE_VERIFIER.full_description:
Allows the holder to make requests of
        package verifiers. Should never be needed for normal apps.

android.permission.ACCOUNT_MANAGER.full_description: Allows the app to make calls to AccountAuthenticators.

android.permission.SET_ANIMATION_SCALE.full_description:
Allows the app to change
        the global animation speed (faster or slower animations) at any time.

android.permission.SET_PROCESS_LIMIT.full_description:
Allows the app
        to control the maximum number of processes that will run. Never
        needed for normal apps.

android.permission.CONTROL_LOCATION_UPDA.full_description:
Allows the app to enable/disable location
        update notifications from the radio.  Not for use by normal apps.

android.permission.MASTER_CLEAR.full_description:
Allows the app to completely
        reset the system to its factory settings, erasing all data,
        configuration, and installed apps.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIMAX_STATE.full_description:
Allows the app to determine whether
     WiMAX is enabled and information about any WiMAX networks that are
     connected.

android.permission.ALLOW_ANY_CODEC_FOR_P.short_description: use any media decoder for playback
android.permission.ALLOW_ANY_CODEC_FOR_P.full_description:
Allows the app to use any installed
        media decoder to decode for playback.

android.permission.SUBSCRIBED_FEEDS_READ.full_description: Allows the app to get details about the currently synced feeds.

android.permission.WRITE_CONTACTS.full_description:
Allows the app to
    modify the data about your contacts stored on your phone, including the
    frequency with which you've called, emailed, or communicated in other ways
    with specific contacts. This permission allows apps to delete contact
    data.

android.permission.BIND_REMOTEVIEWS.full_description:
Allows the holder to bind to the top-level
        interface of a widget service. Should never be needed for normal apps.

android.permission.DELETE_PACKAGES.full_description:
Allows the app to delete
        Android packages. Malicious apps may use this to delete important apps.

android.permission.ACCESS_CHECKIN_PROPER.full_description:
Allows the app read/write access to
        properties uploaded by the checkin service.  Not for use by normal
        apps.

android.permission.DIAGNOSTIC.short_description: read/write to resources owned by diag
android.permission.DIAGNOSTIC.full_description:
Allows the app to read and write to
    any resource owned by the diag group; for example, files in /dev. This could
    potentially affect system stability and security. This should be ONLY be used
    for hardware-specific diagnostics by the manufacturer or operator.

android.permission.BROADCAST_SMS.full_description:
Allows the app to
        broadcast a notification that an SMS message has been received.
        Malicious apps may use this to forge incoming SMS messages.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.full_description:
Allows the app to view information
      about Wi-Fi networking, such as whether Wi-Fi is enabled and name of
      connected Wi-Fi devices.

android.permission.READ_SYNC_SETTINGS.full_description: Allows the app to read the sync settings for an account. For example, this can determine whether the People app is synced with an account.

android.permission.READ_USER_DICTIONARY.short_description: read terms you added to the dictionary
android.permission.READ_USER_DICTIONARY.full_description:
Allows the app to read all words,
       names and phrases that the user may have stored in the user dictionary.

android.permission.CHANGE_COMPONENT_ENAB.full_description:
Allows the app to change whether a
        component of another app is enabled or not. Malicious apps may use this
        to disable important phone capabilities. Care must be used with this permission, as it is
        possible to get app components into an unusable, inconsistent, or unstable state.

android.permission.SET_POINTER_SPEED.full_description:
Allows the app to change
        the mouse or trackpad pointer speed at any time. Should never be needed for
        normal apps.

android.permission.EXPAND_STATUS_BAR.full_description: Allows the app to expand or collapse the status bar.

android.permission.SET_KEYBOARD_LAYOUT.full_description:
Allows the app to change
        the keyboard layout. Should never be needed for normal apps.

android.permission.REORDER_TASKS.full_description:
Allows the app to move tasks to the
      foreground and background.  The app may do this without your input.

android.permission.ASEC_DESTROY.full_description: Allows the app to destroy internal storage.

android.permission.INSTALL_PACKAGES.full_description:
Allows the app to install new or updated
        Android packages. Malicious apps may use this to add new apps with arbitrarily
        powerful permissions.

android.permission.RECEIVE_EMERGENCY_BRO.full_description:
Allows the app to receive
      and process emergency broadcast messages. This permission is only available
      to system apps.

android.permission.READ_SMS.short_description: read your text messages (SMS or MMS)
android.permission.READ_SMS.full_description:
Allows the app to read SMS
      messages stored on your phone or SIM card. This allows the app to read all
      SMS messages, regardless of content or confidentiality.

android.permission.SEND_SMS_NO_CONFIRMAT.short_description: send SMS messages with no confirmation
android.permission.SEND_SMS_NO_CONFIRMAT.full_description:
Allows the app to send SMS
      messages. This may result in unexpected charges. Malicious apps may cost
      you money by sending messages without your confirmation.

android.permission.CLEAR_APP_CACHE.full_description:
Allows the app to free phone storage
        by deleting files in app cache directory. Access is very
        restricted usually to system process.

android.permission.MANAGE_NETWORK_POLICY.full_description: Allows the app to manage network policies and define app-specific rules.

android.permission.DUMP.full_description:
Allows the app to retrieve
        internal state of the system. Malicious apps may retrieve
        a wide variety of private and secure information that they should
        never normally need.

android.permission.READ_SOCIAL_STREAM.full_description:
Allows the app
      to access and sync social updates from you and your friends. Be careful
      when sharing information -- this allows the app to read communications
      between you and your friends on social networks, regardless of
      confidentiality. Note: this permission may not be enforced on all social
      networks.

android.permission.READ_NETWORK_USAGE_HI.full_description: Allows the app to read historical network usage for specific networks and apps.

android.permission.HARDWARE_TEST.full_description:
Allows the app to control
        various peripherals for the purpose of hardware testing.

android.permission.FORCE_BACK.full_description:
Allows the app to force any
        activity that is in the foreground to close and go back.
        Should never be needed for normal apps.

android.permission.WRITE_SECURE_SETTINGS.full_description:
Allows the app to modify the
        system's secure settings data. Not for use by normal apps.

android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW.full_description:
Allows the app to show system
      alert windows.  Some alert windows may take over the entire screen.

android.permission.START_ANY_ACTIVITY.full_description: Allows the app to start any activity, regardless of permission protection or exported state.

android.permission.SUBSCRIBED_FEEDS_WRIT.full_description:
Allows the app to modify
      your currently synced feeds. Malicious apps may change your synced feeds.

android.permission.BROADCAST_WAP_PUSH.full_description:
Allows the app to
        broadcast a notification that a WAP PUSH message has been received.
        Malicious apps may use this to forge MMS message receipt or to
        silently replace the content of any webpage with malicious variants.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.full_description:
Allows the app to view
      information about network connections such as which networks exist and are
      connected.

android.permission.CHANGE_WIMAX_STATE.full_description:
Allows the app to
      connect the phone to and disconnect the phone from WiMAX networks.

android.permission.MOUNT_FORMAT_FILESYST.full_description: Allows the app to format removable storage.

android.permission.BIND_APPWIDGET.full_description:
Allows the app to tell the system
        which widgets can be used by which app. An app with this permission
        can give access to personal data to other apps.
        Not for use by normal apps.

android.permission.INSTALL_LOCATION_PROV.short_description: permission to install a location provider
android.permission.INSTALL_LOCATION_PROV.full_description:
Create mock location sources
      for testing or install a new location provider.  This allows the app to
      override the location and/or status returned by other location sources
      such as GPS or location providers.

android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS.full_description: Allows the app to modify global audio settings such as volume and which speaker is used for output.

android.permission.READ_LOGS.full_description:
Allows the app to read from the
        system's various log files.  This allows it to discover general
        information about what you are doing with the phone, potentially
        including personal or private information.

android.permission.NFC.full_description:
Allows the app to communicate
      with Near Field Communication (NFC) tags, cards, and readers.

android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_MULTICAST.full_description:
Allows the app to receive
      packets sent to all devices on a Wi-Fi network using multicast addresses,
      not just your phone.  It uses more power than the non-multicast mode.

android.permission.GET_DETAILED_TASKS.full_description:
Allows the app to retrieve
        detailed information about currently and recently running tasks. Malicious apps may
        discover private information about other apps.

android.permission.GET_TASKS.full_description:
Allows the app to retrieve information
       about currently and recently running tasks.  This may allow the app to
       discover information about which applications are used on the device.

android.permission.SET_TIME.full_description: Allows the app to change the phone's clock time.

android.permission.CALL_PHONE.full_description:
Allows the app to call phone numbers
      without your intervention. This may result in unexpected charges or calls.
      Note that this doesn't allow the app to call emergency numbers.
      Malicious apps may cost you money by making calls without your
      confirmation.

android.permission.KILL_BACKGROUND_PROCE.full_description:
Allows the app to end
      background processes of other apps.  This may cause other apps to stop
      running.

android.permission.DELETE_CACHE_FILES.full_description:
Allows the app to delete
        cache files.

android.permission.MODIFY_NETWORK_ACCOUN.full_description: Allows the app to modify how network usage is accounted against apps. Not for use by normal apps.

android.permission.ACCESS_MTP.full_description: Allows access to the kernel MTP driver to implement the MTP USB protocol.

android.permission.CLEAR_APP_USER_DATA.full_description: Allows the app to clear user data.

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.full_description:
Access
      approximate location from location providers using network sources such as
      cell tower and Wi-Fi. When these location services are available and turned
      on, this permission allows the app to determine your approximate
      location.

android.permission.BIND_TEXT_SERVICE.full_description:
Allows the holder to bind to the top-level
        interface of a text service(e.g. SpellCheckerService). Should never be needed for normal apps.

android.permission.DEVICE_POWER.full_description: Allows the app to turn the phone on or off.

android.permission.ASEC_RENAME.full_description: Allows the app to rename internal storage.

android.permission.INTERNAL_SYSTEM_WINDO.full_description:
Allows the app to create
        windows that are intended to be used by the internal system
        user interface. Not for use by normal apps.

android.permission.SET_ACTIVITY_WATCHER.short_description: monitor and control all app launching
android.permission.SET_ACTIVITY_WATCHER.full_description:
Allows the app to
        monitor and control how the system launches activities.
        Malicious apps may completely compromise the system. This
        permission is only needed for development, never for normal
        use.

android.permission.BIND_WALLPAPER.full_description:
Allows the holder to bind to the top-level
        interface of a wallpaper. Should never be needed for normal apps.

android.permission.READ_CALENDAR.short_description: read calendar events plus confidential information
android.permission.READ_CALENDAR.full_description:
Allows the app to
       read all calendar events stored on your phone, including those of friends
       or co-workers. This may allow the app to share or save your calendar data,
       regardless of confidentiality or sensitivity.

android.permission.SHUTDOWN.full_description:
Puts the activity manager into a shutdown
        state.  Does not perform a complete shutdown.

android.permission.CHANGE_CONFIGURATION.full_description:
Allows the app to
        change the current configuration, such as the locale or overall font
        size.

android.permission.READ_CONTACTS.full_description:
Allows the app to
      read data about your contacts stored on your phone, including the
      frequency with which you've called, emailed, or communicated in other ways
      with specific individuals. This permission allows apps to save your
      contact data, and malicious apps may share contact data without your
      knowledge.

android.permission.WRITE_SYNC_SETTINGS.full_description: Allows an app to modify the sync settings for an account.  For example, this can be used to enable sync of the People app with an account.

android.permission.CHANGE_BACKGROUND_DAT.full_description: Allows the app to change the background data usage setting.

android.permission.WRITE_GSERVICES.full_description:
Allows the app to modify the
        Google services map.  Not for use by normal apps.

android.permission.ACCESS_LOCATION_EXTRA.full_description:
Allows the app to access
      extra location provider commands.  This may allow the app to to interfere
      with the operation of the GPS or other location sources.

android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO.full_description:
Allows the app to record audio with the
      microphone.  This permission allows the app to record audio at any time
      without your confirmation.

android.permission.READ_PROFILE.full_description:
Allows the app to read
     personal profile information stored on your device, such as your name and
     contact information. This means the app can identify you and may send your
     profile information to others.

android.permission.WRITE_SOCIAL_STREAM.full_description:
Allows the app to
     display social updates from your friends.  Be careful when sharing
     information -- this allows the app to produce messages that may appear to
     come from a friend. Note: this permission may not be enforced on all social
     networks.

android.permission.MOVE_PACKAGE.full_description: Allows the app to move app resources from internal to external media and vice versa.

android.permission.SET_DEBUG_APP.full_description:
Allows the app to turn
        on debugging for another app. Malicious apps may use this
        to kill other apps.

android.permission.BLUETOOTH.full_description:
Allows the app to view the
      configuration of the Bluetooth on the phone, and to make and accept
      connections with paired devices.

android.permission.STATUS_BAR.full_description: Allows the app to disable the status bar or add and remove system icons.

android.permission.WRITE_USER_DICTIONARY.full_description:
Allows the app to write new words into the
      user dictionary.

android.permission.SIGNAL_PERSISTENT_PRO.full_description:
Allows the app to request that the
        supplied signal be sent to all persistent processes.

com.android.alarm.permission.SET_ALARM.full_description:
Allows the app to set an alarm in
      an installed alarm clock app. Some alarm clock apps may
      not implement this feature.

android.permission.READ_INPUT_STATE.short_description: record what you type and actions you take
android.permission.READ_INPUT_STATE.full_description:
Allows the app to watch the
        keys you press even when interacting with another app (such
        as typing a password). Should never be needed for normal apps.

android.permission.WRITE_APN_SETTINGS.full_description:
Allows the app to change network settings and to intercept and inspect all network traffic,
      for example to change the proxy and port of any APN. Malicious apps may monitor, redirect, or modify network
      packets without your knowledge.

android.permission.ACCESS_SURFACE_FLINGE.full_description: Allows the app to use SurfaceFlinger low-level features.

android.permission.SERIAL_PORT.full_description: Allows the holder to access serial ports using the SerialManager API.

android.permission.MANAGE_USB.short_description: manage preferences and permissions for USB devices
android.permission.MANAGE_USB.full_description: Allows the app to manage preferences and permissions for USB devices.

android.permission.PROCESS_OUTGOING_CALL.full_description:
Allows the app to process
      outgoing calls and change the number to be dialed. This permission allows
      the app to monitor, redirect, or prevent outgoing calls.

android.permission.CALL_PRIVILEGED.full_description:
Allows the app to call
        any phone number, including emergency numbers, without your intervention.
        Malicious apps may place unnecessary and illegal calls to emergency
        services.

android.permission.WRITE_CALENDAR.short_description: add or modify calendar events and send email to guests without owners' knowledge
android.permission.WRITE_CALENDAR.full_description:
Allows the app to
     add, remove, change events that you can modify on your phone, including
     those of friends or co-workers. This may allow the app to send messages
     that appear to come from calendar owners, or modify events without the
     owners' knowledge.

android.permission.ACCESS_CONTENT_PROVID.full_description:
Allows the holder to access content
     providers from the shell. Should never be needed for normal apps.

android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS.full_description:
Allows the app to
    perform operations like adding and removing accounts, and deleting
    their password.

android.permission.PERFORM_CDMA_PROVISIO.full_description:
Allows the app to start CDMA provisioning.
        Malicious apps may unnecessarily start CDMA provisioning.

android.permission.WRITE_SMS.short_description: edit your text messages (SMS or MMS)
android.permission.WRITE_SMS.full_description:
Allows the app to write
      to SMS messages stored on your phone or SIM card. Malicious apps
      may delete your messages.

android.permission.RETRIEVE_WINDOW_CONTE.full_description:
Allows the app to retrieve
        the content of the active window. Malicious apps may retrieve
        the entire window content and examine all its text except passwords.

android.permission.READ_FRAME_BUFFER.full_description: Allows the app to read the content of the frame buffer.

android.permission.STOP_APP_SWITCHES.full_description:
Prevents the user from switching to
        another app.

android.permission.CAMERA.full_description:
Allows the app to take pictures and videos
      with the camera.  This permission allows the app to use the camera at any
      time without your confirmation.

android.permission.RESTART_PACKAGES.full_description:
Allows the app to end
      background processes of other apps.  This may cause other apps to stop
      running.

android.permission.BACKUP.full_description: Allows the app to control the system's backup and restore mechanism.  Not for use by normal apps.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.full_description:
Access precise
      location sources such as the Global Positioning System on the phone. When
      location services are available and turned on, this permission allows the
      app to determine your precise location.

android.permission.SET_SCREEN_COMPATIBIL.full_description:
Allows the app to control the
        screen compatibility mode of other applications.  Malicious applications may
        break the behavior of other applications.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.short_description: modify or delete the contents of your SD card
android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.full_description: Allows the app to write to the SD card.

android.permission.ASEC_MOUNT_UNMOUNT.full_description: Allows the app to mount/unmount internal storage.

android.permission.AUTHENTICATE_ACCOUNTS.full_description:
Allows the app
